    dc:description "FIGURES 16–29. Sobarocephala araujoi sp. nov. Holotype ♂ (16–27, 29) and Paratype ♀ (28). 16, habitus, lateral view; 17, head, frontal view; 18, head, lateral view; 19, head and thorax, dorsal view; 20, thorax and abdomen, dorsal view; 21, wing; 22, apex of abdomen, lateral view; 23, terminalia, dorsal view; 24, subepandrial sclerite (outlined), ventral view; 25, hypandrium and phallus, ventral view; 26, hypandrium and phallus, lateral view (ejaculatory apodeme outlined); 27, apex of hypandrium and phallus, lateral view; 28. Paratype ♀, habitus, dorsal view; 29, holotype labels. Abbreviations: basiph = basiphallus; distph = distiphallus; ej apod = ejaculatory apodeme; paraph = paraphallus; phapod = phalapodeme; pregt = pregonite." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8430678/files/figure.png" ;
